---
title: Sweet Chilli Pork Patties with Garlic Rice & Greens
description: Add a nutty flair to your pork rissoles with a moreish sweet chilli and crunchy peanut sauce that adds colour, flavour and a whole lot of fun! Served with garlic rice and stir-fried veggies, this simple meal will please the whole family.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c7f52d9c445fa232d403752-26620507.jpg
